msgstr ""

#: src/ch20-03-advanced-types.md:15
msgid ""
"This section assumes you’ve read the earlier section [“Implementing External "
"Traits with the Newtype Pattern”](ch20-02-advanced-traits.html#implementing-"
"external-traits-with-the-newtype-pattern)<!-- ignore -->. The newtype "
"pattern is also useful for tasks beyond those we’ve discussed so far, "
