"$ cargo run\n"
"   Compiling threads v0.1.0 (file:///projects/threads)\n"
"error[E0373]: closure may outlive the current function, but it borrows `v`, "
"which is owned by the current function\n"
" --> src/main.rs:6:32\n"
"  |\n"
"6 |     let handle = thread::spawn(|| {\n"
