#: src/ch14-02-publishing-to-crates-io.md:256
msgid ""
"Note that the `PrimaryColor` and `SecondaryColor` types aren’t listed on the "
"front page, nor is the `mix` function. We have to click `kinds` and `utils` "
"to see them."
