"directory named for the parent module in these places:"
msgstr ""

#: src/ch07-02-defining-modules-to-control-scope-and-privacy.md:34
msgid ""
"Inline, directly following `mod vegetables`, within curly brackets instead "
"of the semicolon"
msgstr ""

#: src/ch07-02-defining-modules-to-control-scope-and-privacy.md:36
msgid "In the file _src/garden/vegetables.rs_"
msgstr ""

#: src/ch07-02-defining-modules-to-control-scope-and-privacy.md:37
msgid "In the file _src/garden/vegetables/mod.rs_"
msgstr ""

#: src/ch07-02-defining-modules-to-control-scope-and-privacy.md:38
msgid ""
