#: src/ch07-02-defining-modules-to-control-scope-and-privacy.md:168
msgid ""
"Earlier, we mentioned that _src/main.rs_ and _src/lib.rs_ are called _crate "
"roots_. The reason for their name is that the contents of either of these "
"two files form a module named `crate` at the root of the crate’s module "
