"   |\n"
" 3 |         fn add_to_waitlist() {}\n"
"   |         ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^\n"
"\n"
"For more information about this error, try `rustc --explain E0603`.\n"
"error: could not compile `restaurant` (lib) due to 2 previous errors\n"
