"you tell Cargo which external crates your project depends on and which "
"versions of those crates you require. In this case, we specify the `rand` "
"crate with the semantic version specifier `0.8.5`. Cargo understands "
"[Semantic Versioning](http://semver.org)<!-- ignore --> (sometimes called "
"_SemVer_), which is a standard for writing version numbers. The specifier "
"`0.8.5` is actually shorthand for `^0.8.5`, which means any version that is "
"at least 0.8.5 but below 0.9.0."
